<title>USA: Alexion says in deals to raise $11.2 mln.</title>
<headline>Alexion says in deals to raise $11.2 mln.</headline>
<dateline>NEW HAVEN, Conn. 1997-06-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Alexion Pharmaceuticals Inc said Tuesday it has entered into agreements with institutional investors to raise $11.2 million in a private placement of 1.45 million shares of common stock.</p>
<p>The company said it will use proceeds to fund research and development activities and general corporate purposes.</p>
<p>It said the investments are from existing institutional shareholders and new institutional investors. Robertson, Stephens &amp; Co LLC was the placement agent in the deal.</p>
